'''Code Alpha-five-zed-alpha''' was a code within Security Protocol Five that [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] gave to [[R7-T1]] to send to him on Control Channel One in case anyone got too close to [[Darth Vader's Coruscant fortress retreat|Vader's retreat]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Unaware to the [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droid]] was that it would notify Luke to destroy the fortress, sending it and the [[E-7 E-wing multi-role starfighter|E-wing starfighter]] into the [[Great Western Sea/Legends|Western Sea]].

